            ShowInternational();

            ShowInternational();

        //切換成[國外抵達]

        //切換成[國內抵達]

        //切換成[國外起飛]

            ShowIntlDep();

        //切換成[國內起飛]
        $("[id$=aDomSwitchDep]").click(function () {
            ShowDomDep();

        $("[id$=tabF]").focus();

        //國際線起飛
        $("#aIntlDep").blur(function () {
            $("input[id$=ucAirScheduleInfo1_tbKeyword]").focus();            
        });

        //查看所有航班資訊 國際線起飛
        $("a[id$=aViewIntlDept]").blur(function () {
            $("#aIntlSwitchArr").trigger("click");
            $("#aIntlActiveArr").focus();
        });

        $("#aIntlActiveArr").blur(function () {
            $("input[id$=ucAirScheduleInfo2_tbKeyword]").focus();           
        });

        $("#aDomesticDept").blur(function () {
            $("input[id$=ucAirScheduleInfo3_tbKeyword]").focus();

        $("[id$=divDomestic]").hide();
        $("[id$=divIntlArr]").hide();

        //for no script
        $("[id$=aSwitchDom]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aSwitchDom_r]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aSwitchIntl]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aSwitchIntl_r]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aIntlSwitchArr]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aIntlSwitchDep]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aDomSwitchArr]").removeAttr("style");
        $("[id$=aDomSwitchDep]").removeAttr("style");
    }
    function ShowDomestic() {
        $("[id$=divInternational]").hide();
        $("[id$=divDomestic]").show();
        ShowDomDep();
    }
    function ShowInternational() {
        $("[id$=divDomestic]").hide();
        $("[id$=divInternational]").show();
        ShowIntlDep()
    }
    function ShowIntlArr() {
        $("[id$=divIntlDep]").hide();
        $("[id$=divIntlArr]").show();
    }
    function ShowDomArr() {
        $("[id$=divDomDep]").hide();
        $("[id$=divDomArr]").show();
    }
    function ShowIntlDep() {
        $("[id$=divIntlDep]").show();
        $("[id$=divIntlArr]").hide();
    }
    function ShowDomDep() {
        $("[id$=divDomDep]").show();
        $("[id$=divDomArr]").hide();
    }
      </script>

   <script>
    $(function () {
        BindOpenMobileLink();
        $(".flexnav").flexNav();

        $('#navbar-menu .dropdown-menu .flexslider').flexslider({
            animation: "slide",
            animationLoop: false,
            slideshow: false,
            itemWidth: 350,
            itemMargin: 15,
            minItems: 5,
            maxItems: 5
        });

        $('#navbar-menu .dropdown.mega-dropdown').on('shown.bs.dropdown', function () {
            var slider = $(this).find('.flexslider').data('flexslider');
            $(window).trigger('resize');
            slider.resize();
        });

        $("#navbar-menu .dropdown-menu").click(function (e) { e.stopPropagation(); });

        $("#owl-example").owlCarousel({

            navigation: true,
            slideSpeed: 300,
            paginationSpeed: 400,
            autoPlay: false,
            singleItem: true

            // "singleItem:true" is a shortcut for:
            // items : 1, 
            // itemsDesktop : false,
            // itemsDesktopSmall : false,
            // itemsTablet: false,
            // itemsMobile : false

        });

        var w = 0;
        var h = 0;
        $(window).load(function () {
            w = $(window).width();
            h = $(".slider_img").height();
            $(".banner_slide_wrapper").css("height", h);

        });
        $(window).resize(function () {
            var new_w = $(window).width();
            var new_imgHeight = h * (new_w / w);
            //console.log(w + "/" + new_w + "/" + h + "/" + new_imgHeight);
            $(".banner_slide_wrapper").css("height", new_imgHeight);
            w = new_w;
            h = new_imgHeight;
        });
    })

    function BindOpenMobileLink() {
        var mobilePath = "";
        var appUrl = "/kia/";
        var pageurl = location.href.toLowerCase();
        if (pageurl.indexOf("net.kingfor.com.tw") < 0)
            appUrl = "/";

        if (pageurl.indexOf("/english/") >= 0)
            mobilePath = "MobileEnglish";

        if ($("a[id$=aLinkMobile]").length > 0) {
            $("a[id$=aLinkMobile]").attr("href", "javascript:void(0);");
            $("a[id$=aLinkMobile]").bind("click", function () {
                window.open(appUrl + mobilePath, "newwindow", "height=700, width=600, top=0, left=0, toolbar=no, menubar=no, scrollbars=yes, resizable=no, status=no");
            });
        }
    }
   </script>
